Going on a "pick" with Frank and Mike is so much fun and could even be considered educational. They have fun while making a living and you can't beat that! One man's junk is truly anothers treasure and the show helps define the difference while also having fun. Now we pass by cluttered yards and wonder if there is a picker living there.

LOVE ALL THEIR SHOWS, and they are on dvds, so you can really look at the stuff they get, and go back  and pause, and SAY...I had that or you still have it. HUMANS of all ages will enjoy the show, and look at the past. Maybe your kids might start keeping better care of their toys if they saw the shows. PARENTS, please let your kids watch ANY of the pickers shows. I enjoy them, and you can too !!!  SEE for yourself why I gave them 5 stars. NOW what does an old man know about the things they pick OR walk past ?....A LOT is my answer
